  "text": "The changes in observational assessment in this study are smaller than those found in a previous study [CITATION_1] . In that study, all the participants were required to complete one hour of supervised Wii-based training for two weeks, augmented with gradually increasing practice at home, from 30 to 180 minutes per day. Since these treatment doses are much higher than those used here, further research will focus on the amount and frequency of VR gaming treatment.",
